		visible = @v_expjuliaquat < 100
	endparam	
  heading
    text = "Uses 3D spherical coordinates in analogy to 2D polar coordinates for \
            complex numbers. Over 50 variants of triplex algebra are available, \
						including the original White/Nylander version and many more described \
					  on Jason's Softology website \
						(http://softology.com.au/gallery/ \
						gallerymandelbulb.htm). Many are based upon the the formulas of Tad \
					  Boniecki."
